# 📚 RIT Learning Platform

An interactive quiz-based learning platform built with ReactJS, Firebase, and modern web technologies for students of Roorkee Institute of Technology.

## 🚀 Features

- 🔐 User Authentication (Firebase)
- 🧠 Topic-based Quizzes (HTML, CSS, Java, Python)
- 🏆 Leaderboard
- 📊 Progress Tracking
- 📄 Generate PDF Certificates (html2canvas + jsPDF)
- 📺 Video-based Learning Modules

## 🛠 Built With

- ReactJS
- Firebase
- React Router
- html2canvas + jsPDF
- Custom CSS

## 📦 Setup Instructions

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Shubham97080/rit-learning-platform.git
cd rit-learning-platform
npm install
npm start
